tContextImpl, and OutputContextImpl depend on javax.servlet APIs; meaningful servlet-facing coverage needs those types on the test classpath.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, external WebDAV server, environment variable, or system property is known to be required. Prefer in-process tests over network services: exercise WebDAV methods, XML/property/report classes, locator factories, and servlet-facing APIs with lightweight stubs or mocks for servlet requests/responses.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The existing native-image run failure appears to be version/native-runtime behavior in generated tests rather than evidence that a service container is required.\",\n    \"Local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative; servlet-api 2.3 matches the artifact's managed provided dependency, but existing older tests used servlet-api 2.4 successfully.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c078953271effea016a421adeb8308193a5aa926438e48a0d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1483, "output": 829, "cacheRead": 28160, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30472, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782717137527, "responseId": "resp_0c078953271effea016a421ad1fa3081939c745b9961d7db92"}}
